title: Mac Imagenomic Plug Ins [k]
description: Finally!!!! Imagenomic Portraiture, Noiseware Professional and Real Grain plugins for Adobe Photoshop on the Mac. Rar file contains (3) disc images that have been cracked. Simply mount disc images, double click on icon and plugins will automatically install with no serials needed. Currently using all three on a PPC G5 with CS3 Extended. Not sure if they are Intel compatible? Portraiture and Noiseware are without a doubt the two most useful plugins for professional photographers that I have ever used. Enjoy
